rails new coffee_shop

rails g scaffold Item name:string price:float tax_rate:float

rails generate model Order total_price:float 

rails generate model OrderItem item:references order:references

rails g scaffold Discount item_ids:string discount:float discount_amount:float discounted_item_id:integer


APIs

/items   - which will return list of available items with tax_rate
/oders   - all the orders
GET /order/1 - specific order

POST /order - item with quantity create order with no_payment -> response with calculation
PUT /order - update order with payement true - return total price 


POST order
body = {{item_id: 1, quantity: 2},{item_id: 2, quantity: 1}}